Luke, I Am Your ....
Luke Skywalker has family and friends. Help him remind them who is who. Given a string with a name, return the relation of that person to Luke.

Person	Relation
Darth Vader	father
Leia	sister
Han	brother in law
R2D2	droid
Examples
relationToLuke("Darth Vader") ➞ "Luke, I am your father."

relationToLuke("Leia") ➞ "Luke, I am your sister."

relationToLuke("Han") ➞ "Luke, I am your brother in law."

https://edabit.com/challenge/Ac8GiJBAzEJYmcqyF

My Solution

function relationToLuke(name) {
	let starwars = {darth: "Luke, I am your father.",
								 	leia: "Luke, I am your sister.",
									han: "Luke, I am your brother in law.",
									r2d2: "Luke, I am your droid."
								 }
	if ( name === "Darth Vader" ) {
		return `${starwars.darth}`
	}
		if ( name === "Leia" ) {
		return `${starwars.leia}`
	}
		if ( name === "Han" ) {
		return `${starwars.han}`
	}
		if ( name === "R2D2" ) {
		return `${starwars.r2d2}`
	}
}
